obj.opossum.IT.SH <- ShuffleExpression(obj.opossum.IT, "subclass")
obj.opossum.IT.SHA <- ShuffleExpression(obj.opossum.IT, "subclass", ignore_group = TRUE)

obj.mouse.IT.SH <- ShuffleExpression(obj.mouse.IT, "subclass")
obj.mouse.IT.SHA <- ShuffleExpression(obj.mouse.IT, "subclass", ignore_group = TRUE)


obj.opossum.IT <- ClusterSCT(obj.opossum.IT, resolutions = c(1))
obj.opossum.IT.SH <- SCTransform(obj.opossum.IT.SH, vst.flavor = "v2", return.only.var.genes = FALSE, verbose = FALSE) %>%
                     RunPCA(npcs = 30, verbose = FALSE)
obj.opossum.IT.SHA <- SCTransform(obj.opossum.IT.SHA, vst.flavor = "v2", return.only.var.genes = FALSE, verbose = FALSE) %>%
                      RunPCA(npcs = 30, verbose = FALSE)
obj.mouse.IT <- ClusterSCT(obj.mouse.IT, resolutions = c(1))
obj.mouse.IT.SH <- SCTransform(obj.mouse.IT.SH, vst.flavor = "v2", return.only.var.genes = FALSE, verbose = FALSE) %>%
                     RunPCA(npcs = 30, verbose = FALSE)
obj.mouse.IT.SHA <- SCTransform(obj.mouse.IT.SHA, vst.flavor = "v2", return.only.var.genes = FALSE, verbose = FALSE) %>%
                      RunPCA(npcs = 30, verbose = FALSE)
